{"tid":660741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛木梯掟警車　一男子被捕","createTime":"2018-05-11T03:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:14:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5e48f08b4b3dc688086c87b013394592ee0b4f","tid":660741,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"凌晨1時許，一輛「環頭」警車在九龍城區巡邏，途至候王道準備轉出賈炳達道時，突然有一條木梯打橫飛至，擊中警車的右邊車身。警員發現該條三級木梯，為街上一名年約50歲男子掟出，立即落車追截，當場將他擒獲。警員再檢查警車，發現右邊車身有一道長約8吋的花痕。警方以涉嫌「刑事毀壞」將該名男子拘捕，正調查作案動機，初步相信有人飲醉酒肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/187233/%E9%A3%9B%E6%9C%A8%E6%A2%AF%E6%8E%9F%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E9%86%89%E8%B2%93%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F187233%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E6%258E%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2586%2589%25E8%25B2%2593%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&d=yD3%2FTZhwhBCggL3garZgpf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6305cc26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/187233/%E9%A3%9B%E6%9C%A8%E6%A2%AF%E6%8E%9F%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E9%86%89%E8%B2%93%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}